<div style="color:rgb(130, 130, 130); font-size:14px; font-weight:bold; line-height:21px; " ><div id="intro_title" class="mktEditable" ><span style="font-family: helvetica; font-size: 18px;">TriTech Software Systems’ Inform Public Safety Suite Debuts at the APCO International Conference</span><br> <br><span style="font-family: helvetica;"> <span style="font-size: 12px;"><em></em><em></em><em>TriTech’s Inform Solutions provide an integrated workflow throughout its 9-1-1, Computer Aided Dispatch (CAD), Mobile Data, Field Reporting, Records and Jail Management, and Business Intelligence applications</em></span></span><br><span style="color: #828282; font-family: helvetica; font-size: 16px;"><strong> <br> <span style="font-size: 12px;">August 17, 2012</span></strong></span></div>
